Feedback: I think this would be a much larger problem if people were assigned a doctor without their choosing. Luckily, for most people, we have the opportunity to shop around for doctors, and can freely choose a different one if we feel like they aren't connecting with us on a personal level. Doctors are people first, just like everyone else, and if they don't have a compatible personality with their patients, then it isn't going to be the best experience for either person.
